name: Outside Inside Cornhole Table Set
description: A classic carnival game, but shrunk to basecamp size. This cornhole game packs up small to fit in your luggage or backpack, making it perfect for the beach, road trips or camp outings.Includes 2 collapsible folding boards and 8 bean bags.Set up board dimensions are 60 x 34 x 16.5cm.Collapsed size: 34 x 30 x 8cm.Includes instructions and a carrying pouch.
